The paper deals with channel estimation and multi-user detection in the context of G.fast systems, which are broadband communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also deals with issues related to network infrastructure (such as far-end crosstalk), which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves communication systems, which suggests the category cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks). The paper also involves optimization algorithms, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
